{"tid":2167970,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"特斯拉即將“擠下”台積電，進入全球市值TOP10       嗎?","createTime":"2020-08-21T12:25:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T12:25:20.000Z","uid":1086,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b2eea2a75d5e0b66907a98d79bd129620446a4f2","tid":2167970,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:25:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://postimg.futunn.com/2020082100061170e28b3f48f42.png/logo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpostimg.futunn.com%2F2020082100061170e28b3f48f42.png%2Flogo&h=8e2a0ee3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n週四（8月21日），特斯拉再次大漲，股價首次突破2000美金。一夜之間，特斯拉市值飆升230億美金，已經突破3730億美金。特斯拉年初至今，漲幅高達378%。<br />\n<br />\nWedbush分析師Dan Ives還認為2,000美元的目標價是合理的。而他近日更新了目標價至2500美元。前Bernstein分析師、Aegon Asset和Janus Capital前首席執行官Gary Black週四更新了他對特斯拉的估值。他是個著名特斯拉多頭。而他的最新目標價是2700美元。<br />\n<img src=\"https://postimg.futunn.com/2020082100061069cf60f5f2a2f.png/logo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpostimg.futunn.com%2F2020082100061069cf60f5f2a2f.png%2Flogo&h=5f79fcbb&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}